      <li><span class="font-semibold">Lower Carbon Footprint</span>: Reduces the energy and resources required to produce disposable packaging.</li>
      <li><span class="font-semibold">Compliance with Environmental Standards</span>: Meets increasing regulatory and consumer demand for sustainable agriculture practices.</li>
